<title type="html"><![CDATA[2/13 (Sun.) The year of tiger/ impromptu speech (Host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=589&amp;p=612#p612"><![CDATA[
加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... NKSU5MQT09<br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br />Session 1, Chinese New Year<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.cnet.com/how-to/lunar-new-year-the-year-of-the-tiger-2022-explained/">https://www.cnet.com/how-to/lunar-new-y ... explained/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1, This is the Year of Tiger. What do you expect of this New Year?<br />2, How did you spend your Chinese New Year holiday last week?<br />3, What’s your favorite animal?<br />4, Do you believe the year of the animal will affect a person’s life or personality? Give an example? How about western zodiac signs?<br />(The Chinese zodiac: Rat, Ox, Tiger, Rabbit, Dragon, Snake, Horse, Sheep, Monkey, Rooster, Dog and Pig. 鼠、牛、虎、兔、龍、蛇、馬、羊、猴、雞、狗、豬)<br />(The western zodiac: Aries, Taurus, Gemini, Cancer, Leo, Virgo, Libra, Scorpio, Sagittarius, Capricorn, Aquarius, and Pisces. 白羊座、金牛座、雙子座、巨蟹座、獅子座、處女座、天秤座、天蠍座、射手座、摩羯座、水瓶座和雙魚座。)<br /><br />Session 2 ‘impromptu discussion + impromptu speech’ <br />For impromptu discussion time (40 minutes), each person prepares one or two questions for the small group discussion.<br />For impromptu speech time (20 minutes), the host will pick some people to answer his questions. The purpose of impromptu speech (Table topic) is to train the speaker to give a speech without any preparation. <br />Speaking time for each person is about 2 minutes.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Thu Feb 03, 2022 9:13 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
